h3. 24 June, 2006: Testoob 1.1 released

This is a pretty big release - "Download it here":http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=138557

* A Huge number of bugfixes
* Over 4 times faster
* New features are:
** A failed tests summary (incredibly useful)
** A simple Tk GUI progress report
** A better assertRaises
** Profiling support
** Silent running
** Graceful behavior on interrupt (Ctrl-C)
** Optionally skip a command-line test _after_ the command is run

